race.comment: SEARCH HISTORY (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.01 beating Tsu'tey. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to go well again. MONEY MACHINE (1) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten a neck (17.16) behind Sonic Cyclone at this track. Won at his only start from this box. Expected to feature. REDBACK EXPRESS (2) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the money the last five starts, the latest when third (17.29) at this track. Can feature again. JAMS DONUTS (8) was a surprise winner last time, don't underestimate.
